behen</spn>, or saw-leaved centaury.</def> <sd>(b)</sd> <def>The
<spn>Cucubalus behen</spn>, or bladder campion, now called <spn>Silene
inflata</spn>.</def> <sd>(c)</sd> <def>The <spn>Statice limonium</spn>,
or sea lavender.</def>⟦br⟧
